//Pseudocode to sum all Positive Number entered by user
//Do-While Looping Construct

Start
    Declare number, sum, as Integer
    set sum to 0

    Do 
        Prompt the user "Enter a Positive Number"
        Read the Input into number
        
        set sum = sum+number

        while(number>=0)    // Check if number is positive or not
    End
    Print "The Sum of All Positive Number Entered is :",sum
Stop